@startuml
!include ../../style.puml

title Component Tests Check One Node In Context

actor Test
participant athens as "Coordinator"
participant byzantium as "Replica Stub"
participant cyrene as "Replica Stub"

Test -> athens : set("title", "Microservices")
activate athens
athens -> byzantium : replicate write
byzantium --> athens : ack
athens ->x cyrene : replicate write
athens -> athens : quorum reached
athens --> Test : success
deactivate athens

note over athens,cyrene #E6F3FF
Focus:
one bounded component with
controlled collaborators
end note

@enduml
